Print GoF object

Source: R/print.gofobj.R
print.gofobj.Rd

Function to print an object of class 'gofobj'

# S3 method for gofobj
print(x, ...)

Arguments

x

object of class 'gofobj'
...

other

Examples

Y <- network(20, directed = FALSE)[,]

modLSM <- lsm(Y, D = 2)
myGof <- goflsm(modLSM, Y = Y, doplot = FALSE)
print(myGof)
